{
  "stem": "22840.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in some quotes of Tiso, he specifically said there's nothing bad that the Jews will give back to Slovak what they took get away from them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Although, you know, doing well economically doesn't mean that you take back from anybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that was the attitude.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a tremendous amount of bitterness against the Slovaks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For their willingness to participate as quislings, as people who follow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not-- I don't justify the Germans by anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's a very different story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans are guilty in a different way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Slovaks did it from pure hatred.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think they continue doing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Slovakia is a very strongly Catholic country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Catholic Church was never pro-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So although the history in-- in Europe, even till this day, their passion plays in Germany, just clear anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in other places, Europe was always anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would even say they got it with their mother's milk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I am [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very bitter about the fact that the Catholic Church promoted and supported such approach, and other parts of Christianity did not stand up against it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there are places which did stand up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- and we all know about the Danes, and the Dutch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- that was not the story of all Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I had a Dane co-worker, which-- which said that the Danes-- how did he say it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Danes are ashamed that they didn't do enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What an irony.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It followed-- it followed the German-- it followed the German model.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish businesses were identified, were robbed, and not protected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Gentiles were asked not to buy from Jews, who are the suckers of the blood of the Slovak nation, the regular type of German copying.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
